Starting React Native:
*******************************************
=============================================

 Install node and npm
 ------------------------
    terminal --> sudo apt install nodejs
             --> node -v
             --> nmp -v

    Install vscode editor to write code for frontend
    link-->https://code.visualstudio.com/download


Setup Expo-cli:
--------------------
    terminal --> sudo npm install -g expo-cli


Create First Application:
--------------------------
    terminal --> npx create-expo-app First_App
        or
             --> expo init First_App
             --> cd First_App
             --> npx expo start

important steps:
-----------------------
//import libraries to create components

//create component that return some jsx/ simple function

// Create Stylesheet to style the component

//export the file, so that we can use it enywhere in our app